            <history-note id="DLM301148">Subsection <amended-provision>(1)(e)</amended-provision> was <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, as from <amendment-date>1 August 2006</amendment-date>, by section <amending-provision href="DLM374664">23(2)</amending-provision> <amending-leg>Historic Places Amendment Act 2006</amending-leg> (2006 No 33) <amending-instruction>by omitting the words <quote.in quote="1">and branch committees</quote.in></amending-instruction>. <emphasis style="italic">See</emphasis> <citation jurisdiction="nz">section <extref href="DLM374668">26</extref> of that Act</citation> as to the transitional provisions.</history-note>
